data.description: ** SELLER WILL CONSIDER ALL VA BUYERS FOR THE VA ASSUMABLE LOAN OF $ 472,000 AT 4 %. INTEREST RATE. SUBJECT TO BUYERS BEING APPROVED BY THE SELLERS LENDER FOR THE LOAN ** Pet friendly, Central AC, 2 story town home in Ke Aina Kai with a fenced in yard. 3 bedroom, 2.5 bath home with a 2 car garage. Laminate floors throughout the home. Fans in every room. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances. Great facility planning with a dining area & a spacious kitchen counter with bar stools for dining. Doors open into the lanai & the enclosed backyard. Close to schools, parks, restaurants & beautiful beaches. On bus line. OWNER WILL INSTALL A NEW CENTRAL AC SYSTEM PRIOR TO CLOSE. VACANT & EASY TO SEE. USE SHOWING TIME. SHORT NOTICE, SAME DAY APPOINTMENTS OK.
